  "3081280": {
    "name": "无用之人：登神长阶",
    "steam_appid": 3081280,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>加群：715097472 了解最新信息，一起共创游戏！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《无用之人：登神长阶》 是一款受《背包乱斗》(Backpack Battle)启发，使用UE引擎开发的黑暗奇幻风格1v1电子斗蛐蛐自走棋游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，您将有一个完整的背包，可通过在商店购买各种道具（装备，饰品，招式等），搭配出专属的强力流派。特定道具可以融合形成一些无法从商店购买的特殊道具，招式之间也存在相互克制的关系。连招的配置与道具装备的组合将成为你克敌制胜的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081280/extras/5ebf25a44590e8af7a7449a60f79a41b.webp?t=1770957126\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新登场角色「海盗」，作为游戏内的第一位女角色，使用火枪弯刀和灵巧的步法，完成一场致命的舞蹈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以免费角色DLC的形式推出，领取后即可在游戏内解锁使用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081280/extras/a39d07cd4a962fe5ea4504cf501af734.poster.avif?t=1770957126\" width=616 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081280/extras/a39d07cd4a962fe5ea4504cf501af734.webm?t=1770957126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081280/extras/a39d07cd4a962fe5ea4504cf501af734.mp4?t=1770957126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081280/extras/0f67998b9b929aebab3939db256dd936.webp?t=1770957126\" width=616 height=60 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中有多个角色可供选择，「骑士」、「瘟疫医生」、「浪人」、「武将」，以及刚刚登上长阶的「海盗」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们不仅在外观上各具特色，在战斗中也能够展现出不同的风格与策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以通过道具赋予招式各种独特的buff，例如暴击、速度提升和格挡等。招式之间存在克制关系，连招亦是胜利的关键，比如设计巧妙的连招可以让你在破坏对手的架势后，迅速展开连续攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081280/extras/cc2b13cabbf3ce3e9a6e5ac6d3398631.poster.avif?t=1770957126\" width=440 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081280/extras/cc2b13cabbf3ce3e9a6e5ac6d3398631.webm?t=1770957126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081280/extras/cc2b13cabbf3ce3e9a6e5ac6d3398631.mp4?t=1770957126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081280/extras/ae8ade25d99170e2005e71e3b2ef0073.webp?t=1770957126\" width=616 height=60 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每局游戏中您将以击败对手并获得10场决斗的胜利为目标。每一场战斗您面对的都是真实的玩家，游戏将带来如同格斗游戏般血脉喷张的1v1真实战斗体验。游戏采用异步联机的方式，在获取10胜之后，您可以选择继续挑战更强劲的对手，还可以将自己的10胜构筑保存，前往巅峰演武场和来自全球的玩家切磋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中还设有天梯试炼榜，想在榜单上留下自己的名字吗，来挑战吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081280/extras/0dd916d4b018217b5ba7e6d2849d5285.poster.avif?t=1770957126\" width=616 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081280/extras/0dd916d4b018217b5ba7e6d2849d5285.webm?t=1770957126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081280/extras/0dd916d4b018217b5ba7e6d2849d5285.mp4?t=1770957126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081280/extras/dd72c0ce278240ea7c4fbf1426b381b4.webp?t=1770957126\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在商店内购买招式、道具、装备来不断丰富自己的背包，这些道具并不是孤立存在的，特定组合可以产生强大的效果，甚至合成出商店里无法买到的特殊道具或招式。您需要精心选择搭配来构建出一个独特且强力的战斗流派。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081280/extras/5ac2d3a5c51c420c7a5d96c5b5742fc1.poster.avif?t=1770957126\" width=440 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081280/extras/5ac2d3a5c51c420c7a5d96c5b5742fc1.webm?t=1770957126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081280/extras/5ac2d3a5c51c420c7a5d96c5b5742fc1.mp4?t=1770957126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081280/extras/454fe38c034427fe8def1421a5b41a8d.webp?t=1770957126\" width=616 height=60 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前已有5个可选职业，以及接近300种丰富道具、装备和招式，可供选择搭配。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >未来还将持续更新道具、角色、玩法模式以及系统功能，一些有趣的东西正在路上，别忘了关注我们即将发布的更新路线！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081280/extras/1b453a5814eac5378aed864ad3f279b8.poster.avif?t=1770957126\" width=616 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081280/extras/1b453a5814eac5378aed864ad3f279b8.webm?t=1770957126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081280/extras/1b453a5814eac5378aed864ad3f279b8.mp4?t=1770957126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
